Package io.libraft.agent.protocol Description

Representation classes for the RaftAgent wire protocol.

The classes in this package enable Jackson-based serialization and deserialization of RaftRPC messages to and from the libraft-agent JSON wire protocol. It contains:

  • Jackson-annotated DTOs.
  • Jackson JsonSerializer and JsonDeserializer definitions for libraft-core and libraft-agent data-types.
